longBusinessSummary: HanseYachts AG develops, produces, and sells sailing yachts and motorboats in Germany, Spain, France, the United States, the United Kingdom, and internationally. The company offers sailing yachts under the Hanse, Dehler, Moody, Privilege, and Varianta brands; and motor boats under the Sealine and Fjord brands. HanseYachts AG markets its products through franchised dealer network and its own distributorships. The company was founded in 1990 and is headquartered in Greifswald, Germany.
